Testware:

LOGIN:
If wrong format of email is entered,error shows up |OK [InvalidEmailFormatLogin]
-If correct format of email is entered,no error is shown and green check is shown instead |OK [ValidEmailFormatLogin]
-If non existing user tries to login,error shows up |OK [invalidLoginData]
-If  existing user tries to login,user is able to login |OK [validLoginData]


SIGN UP:
-If wrong format of email is entered,error shows up |OK [invalidEmailFormatSignUp]
-If correct format of email is entered,no error is shown and green check is shown instead |OK [ValidEmailFormatSignUp]
-User is able to create a new account |OK [signUp]





